   "value": "(* strict check: full residual against the candidate eigenvalue χ1(u-θ-Mh) suggested by the weak check *)\nstrictCheck = Table[\n   Module[{xv,lhs,ratio,resid},\n     xv = x[λ][{M}];\n     lhs = xv.t[λ][1,1][u]//Simplify;\n     ratio = χ1(u-θ-M h);\n     resid = Simplify[lhs - ratio xv];\n     {λ,M,resid}\n   ],{λ,1,3},{M,0,λ}];\nstrictCheck",
