   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "(* Sanity-check result: the weak check passes trivially (a single well-defined ratio\nχ1(u-θ-Mh) at the nonzero components), but the STRICT check fails - the residual is\nnonzero exactly at the neighbouring weight components (M±1). So x[λ][{M}] is only a\ncommon eigenvector of the B(u)-family (it is a weight vector for Ee[1,1], since B(u)\nis linear in Ee[1,1] alone); it is NOT an eigenvector of the full t[λ][1,1][u], because\nthe companion twist's off-diagonal entries connect neighbouring weight spaces.\nTherefore t_M(u) cannot be read off from x[λ][{M}] directly - we instead take it from\nthe genuine matrix spectrum of t[λ][1,1][u], matching branches to M by demanding\nconsistency with a polynomial solution of the TQ relation below. *)",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* the genuine eigenvalues of t[λ][1,1][u], compared (numerically, several sample points) against\nthe candidate closed form κ1(u-θ-(λ-M)h)+κ2(u-θ-Mh); matching verified as a SET for λ=1..4 *)\nClearAll[tEigenvalue];\ntEigenvalue[λ_,M_][u_] := κ1 (u-θ-(λ-M) h) + κ2 (u-θ-M h);\n\nnumSubst = {κ1->3, κ2->7/2, h->11/10, θ->13/10, u->17/10};\nTable[\n  Module[{guess,actual},\n    guess = Sort[N[Table[tEigenvalue[λ,M][u],{M,0,λ}] /. numSubst]];\n    actual = Sort[N[(Eigenvalues[t[λ][1,1][u]]/.twistSubst) /. numSubst]];\n    {λ, Chop[guess-actual]}\n  ],\n{λ,1,4}]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"638911\" data-output-id=\"5\" data-out-n=\"38\" data-sub-idx=\"4\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"18\" data-sub-start=\"6\" data-sub-end=\"12\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[38]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrkneeo3-9o51ovg\" data-page-width-em=\"10\" data-latex-b64=\"XGJlZ2lue3BtYXRyaXh9MSAmIFxsZWZ0XHswLDBccmlnaHRcfVxcMiAmIFxsZWZ0XHswLDAsMFxyaWdodFx9XFwzICYgXGxlZnRcezAsMCwwLDBccmlnaHRcfVxcNCAmIFxsZWZ0XHswLDAsMCwwLDBccmlnaHRcfVxlbmR7cG1hdHJpeH0=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:4.8em;vertical-align:-2.15em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen\"><span class=\"delimsizing mult\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:2.65em;\"><span style=\"top:-4.65em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:6.8em;\"></span><span style=\"width:0.875em;height:4.800em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"0.875em\" height=\"4.800em\" viewBox=\"0 0 875 4800\"><path d=\"M863,9c0,-2,-2,-5,-6,-9c0,0,-17,0,-17,0c-12.7,0,-19.3,0.3,-20,1\nc-5.3,5.3,-10.3,11,-15,17c-242.7,294.7,-395.3,682,-458,1162c-21.3,163.3,-33.3,349,\n-36,557 l0,1284c0.2,6,0,26,0,60c2,159.3,10,310.7,24,454c53.3,528,210,\n949.7,470,1265c4.7,6,9.7,11.7,15,17c0.7,0.7,7,1,19,1c0,0,18,0,18,0c4,-4,6,-7,6,-9\nc0,-2.7,-3.3,-8.7,-10,-18c-135.3,-192.7,-235.5,-414.3,-300.5,-665c-65,-250.7,-102.5,\n-544.7,-112.5,-882c-2,-104,-3,-167,-3,-189\nl0,-1292c0,-162.7,5.7,-314,17,-454c20.7,-272,63.7,-513,129,-7