  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* full check on a monomial basis f(u)=u^n, n=0,...,λ (legitimate since the functional is\nlinear): normalized raw residue sum vs claimed closed form, λ=1,...,4 *)\nTable[\n  Simplify[\n    (normConst[λ] * 2 Pi I Sum[Residue[μ[λ][u] u^n, {u, θ + h(k-1)}], {k,1,λ+1}])\n      - Sum[(-1)^i Binomial[λ,i] (θ+h i)^n, {i,0,λ}]\n  ],\n  {λ,1,4},{n,0,λ}\n] // Flatten // Union",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"638911\" data-output-id=\"25\" data-out-n=\"98\" data-sub-idx=\"1\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"38\" data-sub-start=\"2\" data-sub-end=\"8\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[98]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrkoxll2-ckjn530\" data-page-width-em=\"12\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRcezBccmlnaHRcfQ==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[98]= \\left\\{0\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
